{"thag1.3:0.1":"Theragatha 1.3 ","thag1.3:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag1.3:0.4":"Kankharevatattheragatha ","thag1.3:1.1":"“Pannam imam passa tathagatanam, ","thag1.3:1.2":"Aggi yatha pajjalito nisithe; ","thag1.3:1.3":"Alokada cakkhudada bhavanti, ","thag1.3:1.4":"Ye agatanam vinayanti kankhan”ti. ","thag1.3:1.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma kankharevato thero gatham abhasitthati. "}